  <h2>🔬&nbsp;What I've Learned (So Far)</h2>
  <p>Rather than prediction, I'm focused on what seems to be emerging in practice—patterns, tensions, and questions worth tracking.</p>
  <p>A recurring theme I’m hearing:</p>
  <p class="quote-block">
    “The real fear isn’t losing jobs to AI. It’s losing agency over how it’s used.”<br>
