    <h2>⚖️&nbsp;Research Ethics and Data Practices</h2>
    <p>This research is conducted independently and follows standard ethical practices for research with human participants (informed consent, anonymity, and data protection). The study was initially prepared for IRB review at Rutgers University but is not currently under IRB oversight. The researcher has completed formal ethics training (CITI Program). All participant data is de‑identified and handled using open‑science and privacy best practices.</p>

